---
title: Oven-Fried Chicken with Creamy Macaroni and Peas
description: Think of this as a twist on fried chicken with mac ’n’ cheese, except lighter and more weeknight-friendly. Instead of a batter, the chicken is coated in panko breadcrumbs and baked in the oven for a crispy crunch without loads of oil. And the pasta is plenty creamy but still packs in some bright green peas. When you’ve got that balance between crowd-pleasing classics and a few wholesome twists, you’re guaranteed a dinnertime win.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/oven-fried-chicken-28b48f47.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/oven-fried-chicken-5b6e037d30006c0175208092-8f925096.pdf
